title: Lunchbox Is Fired Up After Stores Refused To Sell Him Alcohol + Amy’s Friend Dating Dilemma: Dating A Guy Who Games for 8 Hours + Bobby Helps Phone Screener Abby with Her Dating Problem
itunes:title: Lunchbox Is Fired Up After Stores Refused To Sell Him Alcohol + Amy’s Friend Dating Dilemma: Dating A Guy Who Games for 8 Hours + Bobby Helps Phone Screener Abby with Her Dating Problem
description:
Lunchbox is fired up and wants to write up a complaint after they refused to sell him alcohol because his ID was expired. Amy’s friend went on a first date with a guy and loved everything about him…except that he revealed he likes to game for 8 hours at a time. Is that a red flag? We play a round of the ‘Bobby Feud’ to see if the show can guess the most recognizable logos in America. Bobby talks to Phone Screener Abby about getting pre-rejected for dates.
